Pink Dot Formation 2024 粉紅匯聚 2024 源自新加坡Pink Dot嘅重要傳統，今年慶幸雨勢一度減弱下，我哋順利完成呢個簡單而隆重嘅儀式！ Pink Dot HK總監之一梁兆輝先生 @djbrianleung 發表致謝之後，Pink Dot HK籌委，支持機構 彩虹之約代表，聯同3位粉紅大使 黃夏蕙，藍奕邦 @bluepongpong ，周殷廷 @whoisyanting ，以及今年度表演嘉賓，贊助商代表，社區伙伴代表，與現場公眾進行大合照，紀念10周年Pink Dot HK歷史一刻！ Special Thanks to our Emcees @joewongyiucho @laulung @sheisjoya @ivancc2wan ————————— We're thrilled to have successfully held a simple yet meaningful ceremony for Pink Dot HK this year, especially as the rain eased up! After Mr. Brian Leung @djbrianleung, one of our directors, expressed his gratitude, representatives from the Pink Dot HK organizing committee and our partner, Covenant of the Rainbow, joined our three Pink Ambassadors— Lana Wong, Pong Nan and YT. Along with our guest performers, sponsors, community partners, and the paricipants , we captured a memorable group photo to celebrate the 10th anniversary of Pink Dot HK!
